title: City of Corona App
description: The City of Corona app provides simple methods for the community residents to engage and be part of this wonderful community. It provides ways to pay bills, sign up for recreation activities, call departments with one click, as well as Live Video feeds from many traffic cameras throughout the city. Through GPS maps, users of the app will be able to find their way to many official City offices, parks, and other locations. When looking for something to do, a calendar has events with the ability to have push notifications with instant alerts on crime, traffic, events, and more.
